Description: native GTK4 desktop app to manage Claude Code sessions
 Claude Session Manager browses every Claude Code session on your machine in a
 sidebar grouped by project, lets you name and star them, and resumes any of
 them in embedded terminal tabs.
 .
 It is an unofficial community tool, not affiliated with Anthropic, and never
 modifies Claude Code's own session data.
